 Under the Volcano and the writings of Charles Bukowski.    aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Feb 2020) 0aReminiscingxFiction. 0aSuicidal behaviorxFiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aVincent, Paul08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYUP eBook Package 2014-2015z978311067250340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300216462423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300216462.jpg  a978-3-11-067250-3  YUP eBook Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aEBA_FAO